org.opendtacho.DDDQuery.internalData.DataTypes
Class KeyIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  org.opendtacho.DDDQuery.internalData.DataClass
      org.opendtacho.DDDQuery.internalData.DataTypes.KeyIdentifier

public class KeyIdentifier
extends DataClass

A unique identifier of a Public Key used to reference and select the key. It also identifies the holder of the key.
